    "There are larger, more general super-topics and smaller, more specific subtopics.",
    "\"Sports\" is a valid topic in that it represents a concept.",
    "\"Football\" and \"Olympics\" are also topics.",
    "They are not completely distinct from \"Sports\" but rather are sub-topics that fall within sports, i.e., they are child topics of the \"Sports\" parent topic in the topic hierarchy.",
    "Topics also relate to each other to varying degrees."
